  ## subscribe

  Subscribes to messages on the given topic


  ### Params


  - **topic** (<code>String</code>,<code>Array</code>|<code>Object</code>) which topic(s) to subscribe to


  - **options** (<code>Object</code>) options for the MQTT subscription


  - **[callback]** (<code>Function</code>) triggered on suback with (err, granted)


  ### Returns

  - (<code>undefined</code>)

